      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The trades council held its regular\nmeeting last night. There was quite\na large attendance owing to the ques-\nton which came up for discussion.\nThe Musicians union reported that\nthe Stockholm was employing unfair\nmusicians, and the arbitration COM\nmittee was instructed to interview\nMr.. Pearson on the subject."
